title: [PSP] TeleTubies for the Playstation Portable. PS1 to PSP conver
description:

Just put this folder into the PSP/Game directory and all should be ok. 
I have tested it on 3.71 33m-3 custom firmware and It should work upto 3.8 33m-5. 
Not sure on firmware lower or higher than this so you will have to try it for yourself.
Walkthrough and Instruction are included in the DOCUMENT.DAT so please do not delete this file.

Thanks to Marc Lalonde for all documentation.
